headline: Target (NYSE:TGT) Expands TRUBARTM Distribution Across U.S. With Simply Better Brands
summary: Simply Better Brands Corp. began offering its TRUBARTM line in select Target (NYSE:TGT) stores across the country, reflecting the brand’s ongoing expansion. During the past week, Target's stock performance was largely flat, moving in line with broader market trends. Market movements showed positive sentiment influenced by gains in banks and tech stocks, while U.S.-China trade tensions exerted some pressure. Meanwhile, Target's association with new product offerings from Simply Better Brands...
